name: OnCuePlus
0:
”Alexa, ask OnCue Plus to check the status of my generator”
”Does my generator have any active alerts?”
”Check battery voltage of my generator”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: oncue plus
des:
Paired with a standby KOHLER® generator, the OnCue® Plus Assistant will allow you to receive the following

Status of your generator(s)
Active alerts
Last exercise details
Change exercise details
Start/ Stop exercise on your generator(s)
Information on specific parameters like battery voltage, engine temperature and oil temperature of your generator(s)
